* When a child says â€œthis is real,â€
  itâ€™s often because theyâ€™ve **heard adults say it repeatedly**.
* When they insist â€œthis is the only way,â€
  itâ€™s because **other options were never presented**.

This is why the earlier religious rituals begin, the harder they are to untangle.

