## Section 3: â€œNo Indoctrinationâ€ Doesnâ€™t Mean â€œNo Cultureâ€

â€” The Public Value of Multi-Religious Education and the Truth Behind Faith as a â€œSocial Clubâ€

---

### 01 | From â€œNo Indoctrinationâ€ to â€œInformed Awarenessâ€

Opposing **exclusive, unquestionable religious indoctrination** during childhood doesnâ€™t mean removing religion entirely from childrenâ€™s education.

